.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Color: blue, green, red, white, yellow
Nationality: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
Job: security-guard, project-manager, lawyer, fisherman, writer
Cigar: bluemaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
Hobby: gardening, board-games, chess, puzzles, skydiving
1. Nationality:british == Color:red
2. Nationality:swedish == Hobby:chess
3. Nationality:danish == Job:fisherman
4. Color:green is on the left of Color:white
5. Color:green == Job:project-manager
6. Cigar:pall-mall == Hobby:board-games
7. Color:yellow == Cigar:dunhill
8. Job:lawyer is in the middle
9. Nationality:norwegian is on the far left
10. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Hobby:gardening
11. Hobby:skydivings is on the left or right of Cigar:dunhill
12. Cigar:bluemaster == Job:security-guard
13. Nationality:german == Cigar:prince
14. Nationality:norwegian is on the left or right of Color:blue
15. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Job:writer

.:: Answer ::.
